            <item>
             <widget class="QLabel" name="termsContentLabel">
              <property name="text">
               <string>Last updated May 2026

  Terms and Conditions

  Welcome to our Movie Recommendation System (“we,” “our,” or “the Service”). By accessing or using our platform, you agree to comply with and be bound by the following Terms and Conditions.

  1. Use of the Service

  The Service allows users to select their interests (such as genres, actors, or themes) and receive movie recommendations based on those preferences.

  You agree to use the Service only for lawful purposes and in accordance with these Terms.

  2. User Responsibilities

  By using the Service, you agree that you will:

  Provide accurate inputs where applicable
  Not misuse, disrupt, or attempt to interfere with the system
  Not attempt to reverse-engineer or exploit the recommendation algorithm
  Comply with all applicable laws and regulations

  3. Intellectual Property

  All content, features, and functionality of the Service—including design, text, graphics, and algorithms—are owned by us or our licensors and are protected by applicable intellectual property laws.

  You may not copy, modify, distribute, or reproduce any part of the Service without prior written permission.

  4. Recommendations Disclaimer

  The movie recommendations provided by the Service are generated automatically based on user-selected interests.

  We do not guarantee accuracy, completeness, or relevance of recommendations
  Recommendations are for informational and entertainment purposes only
  We are not responsible for user satisfaction with suggested content

  5. Third-Party Content

  The Service may reference or link to third-party movie databases, platforms, or websites.

  We do not control and are not responsible for:

  The content or availability of third-party services
  Any damages or issues arising from their use

  6. Limitation of Liability

  To the fullest extent permitted by law, we shall not be liable for:

  Any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages
  Loss of data, profits, or use resulting from the Service
  Errors, interruptions, or inaccuracies in recommendations

  Use of the Service is at your own risk.

  7. Termination

  We reserve the right to suspend or terminate access to the Service at any time, without prior notice, if you violate these Terms or misuse the platform.

  8. Changes to the Terms

  We may update these Terms and Conditions from time to time. Continued use of the Service after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the updated Terms.

  9. Governing Law

  These Terms shall be governed by and interpreted in accordance with applicable laws, without regard to conflict of law principles.

  10. Contact Information

  If you have any questions about these Terms and Conditions, please contact us at:

  Email: certadev@gmail.com</string>
