            <item>
             <widget class="QLabel" name="privacyContentLabel">
              <property name="text">
               <string>Privacy Policy

  1. Information We Collect

  When you use our Service, we may collect the following types of information:

  a) Information You Provide
  Preferences and interests you select (e.g., genres, actors, themes)
  Optional user inputs such as ratings or feedback

  b) Automatically Collected Information
  Device information (browser type, operating system)
  Usage data (pages visited, interactions within the system)
  Cookies and similar tracking technologies

  2. How We Use Your Information

  We use the collected data to:

  Provide personalized movie recommendations based on your selected interests
  Improve the accuracy and performance of our recommendation algorithm
  Analyze usage trends and enhance user experience
  Maintain and secure the platform

  3. Cookies and Tracking Technologies

  We may use cookies to:

  Remember your selected preferences
  Enhance functionality and user experience
  Analyze system performance

  You can disable cookies through your browser settings, but some features of the Service may not function properly.

  4. Data Sharing and Disclosure

  We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal data. We may share information only in the following cases:

  With service providers who help operate the system (under strict confidentiality)
  If required by law or legal processes
  To protect the rights, safety, and integrity of the Service

  5. Data Storage and Security

  We take appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data against unauthorized access, loss, or misuse. However, no system is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

  6. Data Retention

  We retain your information only as long as necessary to:

  Provide recommendations
  Improve the Service
  Comply with legal obligations

  You may request deletion of your data at any time.

  7. Your Rights

  Depending on your location, you may have the right to:

  Access your stored data
  Request correction or deletion
  Withdraw consent for data processing
  Object to certain uses of your data

  To exercise these rights, please contact us.

  8. Third-Party Links

